column2: In the last month, how often have you been upset because of something that happened unexpectedly?
column3: In the last month, how often have you felt that you were unable to control the important things in your life?
column4: In the last month, how often have you felt nervous and "stressed"?
column5: In the last month, how often have you felt confident about your ability to handle your personal problems?
column6: In the last month, how often have you felt that things were going your way?
column7: In the last month, how often have you found that you could not cope with all the things that you had to do?
column8: In the last month, how often have you been able to control irritations in your life?
column9: In the last month, how often have you felt that you were on top of things?
column10: In the last month, how often have you been angered because of things that happened that were outside of your control?
column11: In the last month, how often have you felt difficulties were piling up so high that you could not overcome them?
